{"tid":1369353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[遍地開花] 旅遊界致香港市民","createTime":"2019-07-26T16:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T17:28:30.000Z","uid":89798,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d48da58d27eba399159e99740eb961fdcb3bd4a2","tid":1369353,"uid":89798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:26:31.000Z","msg":"致香港市民：<br />\n<br />\n我們是一班旅遊業界職員，來自不同公司，不同崗位。<br />\n<br />\n議會一貫的目標是不斷提升業界的專業水平，因此對旅行社、導遊、領隊等都有嚴格要求，竭力令出入境旅客都得到優良服務，提高消費者對旅遊安全和旅遊保障的認識。肩負保障旅客利益和監管所有外遊和入境旅行社的重任。<br />\n<br />\n特區政底自三月推岀逃犯修訂條例以來，一直無視各界的反對聲音。<br />\n過去兩個月，有數以百萬計市民和平上街遊行，以表達訴求。但政府依然漠視民意，堅拒撤回逃犯條例。連串示威期間警察針對示威者濫用權力，以催淚彈及橡膠子彈攻擊示威者及記者，強行驅散市民。<br />\n<br />\n七月二十一日，香港警察在上環驅散示威者，在無任何預警之下，向示威者頭部水平開至少36發橡膠子彈，此舉嚴重超越警察應有的權力。至今警方仍未向公眾交代721的行動詳情。<br />\n<br />\n同日晚上在元朗發生令人震驚的嚴重暴力襲擊，一群白衣暴徒無差別地襲擊市民，包括孕婦、記者及小孩等。而警察竟然選擇性執法，根據多段現場片段顯示，警方不但沒有阻止事情發生，什至視若無賭，警署落閘。<br />\n<br />\n我們對此感到十分痛心及憤怒，身為警務人員竟知法犯法，警黑勾結。<br />\n<br />\n現時巳有11個地區分別對香港發岀旅遊警示，嚴重打擊香港旅遊業發展，為防止社會進一步撕裂，我們懇請政府正視及正面回應我們的訴求。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求如下:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一、全面撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n二、收回612暴動定性 <br />\n三、釋放被捕人士，取消所有抗爭者控罪 <br />\n四、落實真正雙普選<br />\n五、追究警察濫權及成立獨立調查委員會</span><br />\n<br />\n一班愛香港的旅遊業員工上<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#727見<br />\n#一個都不能少<br />\n#香港人一齊走<br />\n#weconnect<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KTQyt4C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKTQyt4C.png&h=e64d261a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3WQOhXY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3WQOhXY.png&h=28d058cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WFveXX0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWFveXX0.png&h=7bfdfb2c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKfyt4G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKfyt4G.png&h=3f977bc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h4wUXX3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh4wUXX3.png&h=6157c231&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eijn6Rp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Feijn6Rp.png&h=fce5be7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vtKGCX6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvtKGCX6.png&h=01e44882&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bf5KAKO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbf5KAKO.png&h=4f670c7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uPozXX9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuPozXX9.png&h=f0e5c215&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ravR0bw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FravR0bw.png&h=a7113b97&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b34ab19b83bb08cfc83a75b878ca781eced26be2","tid":1369353,"uid":254374,"like":0,"dislike":26,"score":-26,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:27:11.000Z","msg":"旅遊界有咩用"},{"pid":"5d133b0183c48b7943f141a681aeeb9cd73d181c","tid":1369353,"uid":259993,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:27:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad0fb97ea9dca29d6ee77ae799ed3152e17ace9a","tid":1369353,"uid":286781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:27:30.000Z","msg":"【投拆Hi】一人一信繼續投訴999，on L 9<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1368627\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1368627</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"09236a2a69b538233a82689d7e24c5de91415eff","tid":1369353,"uid":51701,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"b34ab19b83bb08cfc83a75b878ca781eced26be2","tid":1369353,"uid":254374,"like":0,"dislike":26,"score":-26,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:27:11.000Z","msg":"旅遊界有咩用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:27:40.000Z","msg":"有用過你個回覆"},{"pid":"a83bccb26eb6cebccc2d681aa3e17b85d8581adb","tid":1369353,"uid":252732,"